<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
    <head>
        <title></title>
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
        <style type="text/css">
            * { margin:0; padding:0;}
            @media screen and (min-width:240px) {
                html, body{
                    font-size:9px;
                }
            }
            @media screen and (min-width:320px) {
                html, body{
                    font-size:12px;
                }
            }
            @media screen and (min-width:480px) {
                html, body{
                    font-size:18px;
                }
            }
            @media screen and (min-width:640px) {
                html, body{
                    font-size:24px;
                }
            }
            @media screen and (min-width:960px) {
                html, body{
                    font-size:36px;
                }
            }
            table {
                border-collapse: collapse;
                border-spacing:10px;
                width:100%;
                line-height:22px;
                font-size:12px;
            }
            tr,td {
                border: 1px solid gainsboro;
                background: white;
            }
            td {
                /*	padding:1px 2px;*/
            }
            .con{
                border: 0px;
                border-collapse:separate;

            }
            .noborder{
                border:0px;
                width: 100px;
            }
            img{
                width: 100px;
                height: 50px;
                vertical-align: middle;
                margin-right: 5px;
            }
            .midtd{
                width:50%;
                text-align:center;
                height:35px;
            }
        </style>
    </head>
    <body style="background:#f0f0f0;height:100%;">
        <div style="position:absolute;height:100px;left:0px;right:0px;top:10px;">
            <div style="text-align:center;">
                <img src="${cancelinfo.img}" />
            </div>
            <div style="text-align:center;"><span>${cancelinfo.title}</span></div>
            <div style="margin:1rem;"><hr /></div>
        </div>
        <div style="position:absolute;top:115px;bottom:55px;left:10px;right:10px;">
            <table>
                <tr>
                    <td class="midtd">免责取消时限</td>
                    <td class="midtd">${cancelinfo.cancelcount}分钟</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td class="midtd">免责等待时限</td>
                    <td class="midtd">${cancelinfo.watingcount}分钟</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td class="midtd">取消费用</td>
                    <td class="midtd">${cancelinfo.price}元</td>
                </tr>
            </table>
        </div>
        <div style="position:absolute;bottom:40px;left:5px;right:5px;font-size:14px;">
            <span>
             	备注：<br/>
				1、下单后，无接单应答，乘客<span style="color:orange;">可免责取消</span>。<br/>
				2、在免责取消时限内，乘客<span style="color:orange;">可免责取消</span>。<br/>
				3、免责等待时限：乘客迟到时长超过该时限后，取消订单，乘客有责。
            </span>
        </div>
    </body>
</html>